Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准雅宋_GBK\an7\bord0\frz270\fs19\c&H000000&\b1\pos(57,130)}佛祖朝地狱垂下蜘蛛丝的时候，\N键陀多是怎么看待地狱这地方的？\N请具体回答。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:48.89,Comment,,0,0,0,,哇…这个真好看…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:49.56,Comment,,0,0,0,,真好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.10,Comment,,0,0,0,,太羡慕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来 我也能打破新纪录了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:33.37,Comment,,0,0,0,,三号线列车即将到站
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:37.29,Comment,,0,0,0,,请站到黄线后方等候 注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\an7\bord0\fs30\fsp5\c&H4A4A4A&\b0\frz349.9\move(359,715,379,575)}小晶辛苦了!\N今天要来上班吧?\N那图是我刚好拍到\N店长滑倒wwwww
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\an7\bord0\fs30\fsp5\c&H4A4A4A&\b0\frz349.9\pos(383,567)}小晶辛苦了!\N今天要来上班吧?\N那图是我刚好拍到\N店长滑倒wwwww
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,上次我偷拿了姐姐的指甲油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,被狠狠地骂了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 下一班公交还得等上一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你这个奇怪的钥匙环是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哦? 你不知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有了这个「Muki彦」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就能和喜欢的人搞好关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,四班的琪拉拉就靠着它成功换了座位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,坐到直人身边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,琪拉拉原来喜欢的是直人?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…你别说出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,说得我也想要一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里买的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这 个 嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体 第二版\bord4\fs40\c&HB0700D&\3c&HC2B3AA&\b1\pos(845,266)}全五种{\c&H7533B2&} +?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs18\c&HAB8D9A&\pos(523,371)\frz0.6575}超稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体 第二版\bord4\fs40\c&H602981&\3c&HA1897E&\b1\pos(454,412)\frz2.294}小丸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体 第二版\bord3\fs35\c&H0A5283&\3c&H9A8882&\b1\frz6.328\pos(491,571)}钥匙环!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs35\c&H201411&\frz29.46\pos(989,425)}扭蛋。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Muki…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底要抽多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,话说你抽这么多干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,拿全了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,只差一个超稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,重复的你拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:54.74,Comment,,0,0,0,,下一站…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,补习什么的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,现国
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,训练加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,再跑一轮就差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,晶!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我…跑不动了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 等等我!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 你跑太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么每次都跑这么快?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯? 因为很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,跑起来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵里都是风的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,整个人就像融入了天空似的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:12:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…我似乎能理解你的感受…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,晶!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,上面!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,接着!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\an7\bord0\fs25\c&H787C7E&\frz338\pos(578,235)}我们的友情\N不止于田径\N不是吗{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\an7\bord0\fs30\c&H787C7E&\frz355.8\pos(797,332)}遥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然得分开一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们还会走到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 你家毕竟就在这附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,眼镜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实经常来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不过因为不是这里的市民 所以借不走就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,橘你来这里是…为了作业?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我是来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,找找书的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,纯文学方面的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,橘你也喜欢纯文学?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也不会大声喧哗了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:16.06,Comment,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么推荐的书吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有什么觉得我该读的书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,平常看得不多?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,书这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是经别人推荐就会去读的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不经常读的人尤其如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那本书不适合自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,读下去就会变成一件痛苦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就会变得讨厌书了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:16:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 平常不太读书的你现在来到了图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那就说明 或许有某一本书正在召唤着你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,而这本书 一定是现在的你所需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,幸运的是 这里是横滨最大的图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可说是书的海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一定有你想找的书的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能选错了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想知道他喜欢什么书而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,书的海洋…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,说是海洋…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说是水族馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正行楷_GBK\fs38\bord0\c&H886F2A&\frz251\pos(791,49)}少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正行楷_GBK\fs38\bord0\c&H886F2A&\frz248.7\pos(812,120)}少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正行楷_GBK\fs38\bord0\c&H886F2A&\frz245.8\pos(822,200)}少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,想更多地了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么推荐的书吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,再怎么说也是我自作多情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,看影集…算不上读书的范畴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,橘?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我差不多回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你淘了些什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目漱石的「少爷」和一本影集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 「少爷」不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,店长你要读点什么吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你一起借了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,既然机会难得 那我就恭敬不如从命了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准雅宋_GBK\bord0\c&H231F19&\pos(1054,573)\frz275.4}波起窗畔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正准雅宋_GBK\bord0\c&H21150F&\frz275.4\pos(698,460)}九条千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就这本吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就这三本对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 出借时长两周
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还书时请到这边的返还窗口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,拿好你的书
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那…谢谢你帮我借书
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,被召唤的人 原来是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那就说明 或许有某一本书正在召唤着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而这本书 一定是现在的你所需要的
